%3EIn%20the%20finale%2C%20Catherine%20finally%20tells%20her%20side%20of%20the%20story%3A%20She%20and%20Jonathan%20never%20had%20an%20affair.%20Rather%2C%20he%20broke%20into%20her%20hotel%20room%2C%20threatened%20her%20and%20her%20sleeping%20son%20with%20a%20knife%2C%20and%20then%20repeatedly%20raped%20her.%20The%20erotic%20photos%20Nancy%20discovered%20weren't%20mementos%20of%20their%20relationship%2C%20but%20rather%20images%20that%20Jonathan%20forced%20a%20traumatized%20Catherine%20to%20pose%20for%20during%20the%20violent%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECatherine%20says%20she'd%20collected%20physical%20evidence%20of%20her%20rape%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20go%20to%20the%20police%20but%20chose%20to%20destroy%20it%20and%20bury%20the%20truth%20after%20Jonathan%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222557%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Leila%20George%20in%20%26quot%3BDisclaimer%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672e79ea5ec9bfa3d63cdf81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeila%20George%20in%20%26quot%3BDisclaimer.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EApple%20TV%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bflashbacks%26quot%3B%20we'd%20seen%20earlier%20in%20the%20season%2C%20showing%20Catherine%20as%20a%20sex-starved%20cougar%20and%20Jonathan%20as%20her%20hapless%20prey%2C%20were%20not%20flashbacks%20at%20all.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20enactments%20of%20Nancy's%20imagined%20(and%20ultimately%20false)%20version%20of%20what%20happened%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%2C%20at%20first%20unwilling%20to%20believe%20that%20his%20dead%20son%20was%20actually%20a%20rapist%2C%20commences%20with%20his%20plan%20for%20revenge.%20He%20leaves%20a%20barely%20conscious%20Catherine%2C%20who%20he'd%20already%20given%20drugged%20tea%2C%20and%20goes%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20kill%20her%20estranged%20son%2C%20Nicholas%2C%20now%20a%20drug-addicted%20young%20man%20who's%20in%20intensive%2