d%20what%20would%20be%20shown.%20Those%20scenes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20were%20very%20finely%20detailed%20in%20the%20script%2C%20which%20Cuar%C3%B3n%20showed%20her%20before%20she%20agreed%20to%20sign%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20George%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20know%20that%20any%20sex%20scenes%20she%20was%20doing%20were%20essential%20to%20the%20story%20and%20not%20gratuitous.%20%26quot%3BFor%20this%20job%20in%20particular%2C%20I%20think%20the%20whole%20story%20revolves%20around%20this%20evening%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20vital%20to%20the%20story.%20There's%20nothing%20in%20it%20that's%20not%20needed%20there.%20It%20felt%20very%2C%20very%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20Louis%20Partridge%2C%20who%20plays%20Jonathan%2C%20worked%20with%20intimacy%20coordinator%20Samantha%20Murray%20for%20roughly%20a%20week%20prior%20to%20filming%20the%20intimate%20scenes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20safe%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20following%20the%20moves%20that%20you've%20pre-planned%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said%2C%20likening%20coordinated%20sex%20scenes%20to%20fight%20scenes%20or%20dance%20scenes.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20did.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Louis%20Partridge%20as%20Jonathan%20Brigstocke%20and%20Leila%20George%20as%20Catherine%20Ravenscroft%20in%20%26quot%3BDisclaimer.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672e797a5ec9bfa3d63cde14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELouis%20Partridge%20and%20Leila%20George%20in%20%26quot%3BDisclaimer.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EApple%20TV%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20helped%20that%20she%20and%20Partridge%20built%20a%20rapport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20depends%20so%20much%20on%20the%20other%20person%2C%20and%20who%20you're%20working%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said%2C%20adding%20of%20Partridge%2C%20