20card%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20my%20pick%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%3Ebest%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20applied%20and%20was%20approved%20for%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-chase-card%5C%22%3Ebest%20Chase%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20offered%20a%20ton%20of%20travel%20benefits%2C%20which%20at%20the%20time%20included%20a%20sign-up%20bonus.%20(Depending%20on%20when%20you%20apply%2C%20Chase's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-current-credit-card-signup-bonuses%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%20bonuses%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20even%20higher%20than%20they%20were%20back%20then.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20I%20qualify%20for%20this%20card%2C%20but%20a%20very%20good%20credit%20score%20has%20helped%20me%20secure%20relatively%20low%20interest%20rates.%20Any%20time%20I've%20been%20unable%20to%20pay%20the%20full%20statement%20balance%20over%20the%20years%2C%20interest%20has%20accumulated%2C%20but%20the%20lower%20interest%20rate%20has%20translated%20to%20my%20paying%20less%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20very%20good%20score%20also%20gives%20me%20options%20about%20where%20I%20live.%20Between%20my%20husband's%20job%20and%20graduate%20school%2C%20we've%20moved%20frequently%20over%20the%20last%20six%20years.%20Each%20time%20we%20moved%2C%20we%20had%20to%20apply%20to%20live%20in%20a%20new%20apartment.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20strong%20score%2C%20being%20approved%20for%20an%20apartment%20wasn't%20too%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20finally%20reached%20our%20goal%20of%20buying%20our%20first%20house.%20Not%20only%20did%20our%20high%20credit%20scores%20help%20us%20get%20approved%20for%20a%20mortgage%20%E2%80%94%20they%20also%20helped%20us%20snag%20a%20relatively%20low%20%3Ca%20href%