ged%20plot%20ordered%20by%20Iran's%20elite%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20Corps%20to%20assassinate%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20said%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-charges-iranian-man-in-plot-to-assassinate-donald-trump-6975686%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Dating%2C%20Babies%3A%20South%20Korea's%20'4B'%20Movement%20Enters%20US%20After%20Trump's%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20women%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20%26quot%3Bswearing%20off%20men%26quot%3B.%20Reason%3F%20Donald%20Trump's%20win%20as%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Donald%20Trump%20becoming%20the%20US%20President%2C%20fears%20have%20raised%20over%20the%20abortion%20rights%20of%20women%2C%20doubting%20if%20the%20Republican%20would%20make%20access%20to%20the%20procedure%20more%20uncertain.%20In%202022%2C%20Trump%20had%20celebrated%20the%20Supreme's%20Court's%20ruling%20that%20ended%20a%20nationwide%20right%20to%20abortion.%20However%2C%20over%20time%2C%20he%20has%20also%20said%20that%20he%20would%20leave%20the%20decision%20on%20abortion%20rights%20to%20the%20states%20rather%20than%20enact%20a%20federal%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20rising%20fear%2C%20South%20Korea's%20'4B'%20movement%20has%20entered%20the%20US%2C%20with%20some%20women%20on%20social%20media%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20tired%20of%20awaiting%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20their%20own%20bodily%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'4B'%20movement%20-%20a%20radical%20feminism%20movement%20against%20patriarchy%20-%20origniated%20from%20South%20Korea%20around%202017-18%2C%20but%20gained%20recognition%20in%202019%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%20It%20began%20in%20response%20to%20high%20rates%20of%20violence%20against%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'4B'%20stands%20for%20four%20Koreans%20words%20beginning%20with%20%26quot%3Bbi%26quot%3B%20(which%20translates%20to%20no).%20The%20words%20are%3A%20%26quot%3Bbihon%26quot%3B%20means%20no%20heterosexual%20marriage%2C%20%26quot%3Bbichulsan%26quot%3B%20(no%20childbirth)%2C%20%26quot%3Bbiyeonae%26quot%3B%20(no%20dating)%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bbisekseu%26quot%3B%20(no%20heterosexual%20sexual%20relationships).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20movement%20refuse%20to%20date%2C%20marry%2C%20have%20sexual%20relations%2C%20or%20carry%20babies%20with%20men.%20By%20doing%20this%2C%20the%20women%20are%20pressing%20that%20if%20the%20violence%20or%20inequality%20against%20them%20does%20not%20stop%2C%20they%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20birth%20rate%20will%20drop%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20also%20functions%20as%20an%20online%20community%20where%20women%20engage%20in%20open%20discussion%20about%20navigating%20and%20envisioning%20a%20future%20without%20men.%20Women%20also%20use%20the%20platform%20to%20vent%20their%20frustrations%20and%20concerns%20about%20living%20in%20a%20conservative%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20new%20lifestyle%20focused%20on%20building%20safe%20communities%2C%20both%20online%20and%20in-person.%20What%20we%20want%20is%20not%20to%20be%20labeled%20simply%20as%20some%20man's%20wife%20or%20girlfriend%2C%20but%20to%20have%20the%20independence%20to%20be%20free%20from%20the%20societal%20expectations%20that%20often%20limit%20women's%20potential%20to%20be%20fully%20acknowledged%20as%20human%20beings%2C%26quot%3B%20Haein%20Shim%2C%20a%20South%20Korean%20activist%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20US%20women%20are%20saying%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20seems%20to%20be%20divided%20over%20the%20'4B'%20movement%20in%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLadies%2C%20I'm%20being%20so%20fr%20when%20I%20say%20this%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20close%20off%20your%20wombs%20to%20males.%20This%20election%20proves%20now%20more%20than%20ever%20that%20they%20hate%20us%20and%20hate%20us%20proudly.%20do%20not%20reward%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BReminder%20that%20the%204B%20movement%2C%20and%20the%20separatist%20movement%20in%20general%2C%20isn't%20just%20about%20avoiding%20men-it's%20also%20about%20supporting%20and%20investing%20in%20women.%20Seek%20out%20relationships%20with%20women%2C%20women-owned%20businesses%2C%20women-made%20media%2C%20etc%3B%20surround%20yourself%20with%20women%20and%20our%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20people%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20movement%20would%20never%20work%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731091740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fdr19ilj_abortion-rally-_625x300_25_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F4b-movement-why-some-us-women-are-boycotting-men-after-donald-trumps-win-us-president-6975944%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Donald%20Trump%20becoming%20the%20US%20President%2C%20fears%20have%20raised%20over%20the%20abortion%20rights%20of%20women%2C%20doubting%20if%20the%20Republican%20would%20make%20access%20to%20the%20procedure%20more%20uncertain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F4b-movement-why-some-us-women-are-boycotting-men-after-donald-trumps-win-us-president-6975944%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Northeast's%20Biggest%20Insurgent%20Group%20Threatens%20To%20End%2027-Year-Old%20Ceasefire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20northeast's%20largest%20insurgent%20group%20NCSN(IM)%20has%20threatened%20to%20resume%20%26quot%3Bviolent%20armed%20resistance%26quot%3B%2027%20years%20after%20it%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20India%20over%20allegations%20that%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bbetrayed%26quot%3B%20a%20landmark%20agreement%20signed%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSCN(IM)%20in%20a%20statement%20proposed%20the%20intervention%20of%20a%20third-party%20to%20resolve%20India's%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D124221%5C%22%3E2015%20Framework%20Agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20failing%20which%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bresume%20the%20violent%20armed%20resistance%20against%20India%20for%20defending%20Nagalim's%20unique%20history%20and%20her%20sovereign%20existence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insurgent%20group%20headquartered%20in%20Nagaland%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20it%20meant%20by%20%26quot%3Bthird-party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThuingaleng%20Muivah%2C%20the%2090-year-old%20chief%20of%20the%20National%20Socialist%20Council%20of%20Nagaland%20(Isak-Muivah)%2C%20or%20NSCN(IM)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20alleged%20India%20has%20not%20kept%20its%20word%20on%20recognising%20the%20%26quot%3BNagalim%20national%20flag%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BNagalim%20constitution%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20signed%20in%20August%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202015%20Framework%20Agreement%20was%20billed%20as%20a%20major%20breakthrough%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Mr%20Muivah%20and%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20Indian%20officials%20and%20NSCN(IM)%20members%20sharing%20a%20stage%20for%20the%20camera%20after%20signing%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20content%20of%20the%20agreement%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20released%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fom733rfg_nscn_625x300_08_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20sign%20of%20strain%20in%20the%20post-2015%20talks%20process%20came%20when%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20alleged%20India%20refused%20to%20recognise%20the%20'Nagalim%20sovereign%20national%20flag'%20and%20the%20'Nagalim%20sovereign%20national%20constitution'%2C%20which%20to%20this%20day%20remain%20unsolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20understand%20that%20Nagalim%20and%20the%20NSCN%20have%20given%20India%20the%20finest%20opportunity%20to%20resolve%20the%20decades%20old%20Indo-Naga%20political%20conflict%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20officially%20signed%20Framework%20Agreement%20of%20August%203%2C%202015%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Muivah%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20NSCN(IM)%2C%20said%20in%20a%20five-page%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muivah%20then%20alleged%20that%20India%2C%20however%2C%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20betrayed%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20of%20August%203%2C%202015%20by%20refusing%20to%20recognise%20and%20acknowledge%20the%20Nagalim%20sovereign%20national%20flag%20and%2C%20Nagalim%20sovereign%20national%20constitution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Nagalim%20and%20the%20NSCN%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20wait%20forever%20for%20the%20GoI%20%5Bgovernment%20of%20India%5D%20to%20respect%20and%20honour%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Framework%20Agreement...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20conclude%20and%20realise%20an%20honourable%20political%20agreement%2C%20we%20rule%20out%20peaceful%20means%20against%20the%20ignominious%20betrayal%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20by%20the%20GoI.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20%EF%AC%81rst%20place%20we%20propose%20a%20third-party%20intervention%20to%20resolve%20the%20betrayal%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Framework%20Agreement...%20but%20if%20such%20a%20political%20initiative%20is%20rejected%20by%20the%20GoI%2C%20the%20NSCN%20shall%20resume%20the%20violent%20armed%20resistance%20against%20India%20for%20defending%20the%20Nagalim%20unique%20history%20and%20her%20sovereign%20existence%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Muivah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F789753916%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-XGwV6qIbxmM4SvDY8gml%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7068965517241379%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22NSCN(IM)%20Statement%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Muivah's%20statement%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSCN(IM)%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20India%20in%20October%201997.%20Since%20then%2C%20over%20600%20rounds%20of%20political%20negotiations%20have%20taken%20place%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%20Two%20major%20agreements%20have%20been%20signed%20over%20the%20years%20-%20first%20during%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20time%2C%20and%20the%20second%20in%202015%2C%20a%20year%20into%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20was%20Isak%20Chishi%20Swu%2C%20who%20died%20in%20June%202016%20at%20age%2087%20of%20multi-organ%20failure.%20Swu%20along%20with%20Mr%20Muivah%20formed%20the%20armed%20group%20in%201980%2C%20opposing%20the%20Shillong%20Accord%20signed%20by%20the%20then%20Naga%20National%20Council%20(NNC)%20with%20the%20central%20government%20for%20bringing%20peace%20in%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20military%20analysts%20have%20speculated%20of%20an%20'attrition'%20strategy%20to%20handle%20the%20NSCN(IM).%20As%20senior%20leaders%20die%20of%20age%2C%20the%20younger%20replacements%20may%20be%20less%20rigid%2C%20or%20the%20group%20may%20break%20into%20further%20smaller%20splinters%20amenable%20to%20lasting%20peace%20und