men-led%20organisations%20like%20Shakti%20Shalini%20and%20Udan%20Women%20Empowerment%20Society%20exemplify%20this%20by%20focusing%20on%20fortifying%20leadership%20and%20establishing%20robust%20administrative%20systems%20for%20survivors%20of%20gender-based%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20we%20have%20used%20the%20funds%20to%20cover%20salaries%20for%20management%20and%20operational%20expenses%20at%20Pehchan%2C%20our%20shelter%20home%20for%20women%20in%20distress.%20This%20has%20included%20healthcare%20for%20residents%2C%20travel%20costs%20for%20both%20the%20team%20and%20residents%2C%20and%20part%20of%20the%20funds%20were%20allocated%20to%20routine%20repairs%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Anjali%20Thakur%20from%20%3Cem%3EShakti%20Shalini%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20highlights%20a%20successful%20case%20study%20where%20the%20organisation%20secured%20a%20corporate%20funder%20to%20support%20the%20well-being%20needs%20of%20counsellors%20who%20worked%20tirelessly%20amidst%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20to%20help%20survivors%20of%20gender-based%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdan%20Women%20Empowerment%20Society%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grassroots%20organisation%20in%20Mandsaur%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20has%20also%20strategically%20used%20Rebuild%E2%80%99s%20flexible%20funding%20to%20cover%20honorariums%20for%20its%20team%2C%20renew%20its%20website%2C%20purchase%20Tally%20software%20for%20financial%20management%2C%20and%20manage%20expenses%20incurred%20during%20office%20visits%20for%20evaluating%20the%20accounting%20practices%20of%20partner%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20efforts%20demonstrate%20how%20flexible%20funding%20is%20strengthening%20operational%20efficiency%20and%20sustaining%20vital%20community-driven%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResilience%20defines%20women-led%20organisations%E2%80%99%20journeys.%20Rita%20Mishra%20of%C2%A0Patang%C2%A0encapsulates%20this%20sentimen