%20and%20then%20returning%20the%20clean%20blood%20to%20the%20body.%20Typically%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20necessary%20when%20kidney%20function%20declines%20significantly%2C%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20natural%20filtration%20is%20insufficient%20to%20support%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20problem%20of%20accessibility%20remains%2C%20the%20other%20concern%20is%20affordability.%20To%20provide%20dialysis%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Programme%20(PMNDP)%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%20April%202016.%20The%20programme%20has%20two%20components%3A%20Hemodialysis%20(HD)%20services%20and%20Peritoneal%20dialysis%20(PD)%20services.%20Under%20the%20PMNDP%2C%20the%20government%20has%20set%20up%201%2C530%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20still%20leaving%20a%20significant%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKey%20issues%20include%20high%20treatment%20costs%2C%20limited%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344858%2Fthe-hans-foundation-dialysis-chronic-kidney-disease-renal-care-centre-treat-underprivileged-rural-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accessibility%20barriers%20for%20patients%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20healthcare%20professionals.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20kidney%20disease%20and%20dialysis%20options%20further%20complicates%20timely%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20Dialysis%20Convenient%3A%20How%20VitusCa